    <thetext>Consumers of @TestFixture@ outside of Mylyn may want to use other credentials then the default Mylyn test credentials. In order to do this, several calls in TestFixture need to be overriden to inject the right credentials. We should pull out the credential retrieval in one protected method so other fixtures can easily provide the right credentials without intercepting other calls.</thetext>
